<br>
<br>
  We cleared all the spiders out of the area then set op on the north wall.  I zoned in and popped the event. We had 3 bards on the raid. Each bard pre-targeted 2 mezzable minions. so that was 6 mobs to be locked down.<br>
<br>
 Then we had 2 pallys and a druid get agro and start kiting the minions..  the bards plucked their targets out of the mess while kiters continused..  once bards had theirs locked the kiters  started Rooting the rest of the minions.<br>
<br>
 As soon as we had most of the minions under control the rest of the raid charged in and started killing the Lichs, we had one cleric doing nothing but dragging and rezzing ppl that got killed in the beginign chaos.<br>
<br>
  Once we got to the last lich the MA( lvl 70sk) pulled off at 20% and got ready for the erudite to pop.  we chose to keep him pinned on the ramp and hide the casters/healers on the back side of the ramp.  Once the erudite hit 10% ALL the melees pulled off and hid with the healers/casters  leaving the dots and SK to finish the erudite.<br>
<br>
 Soon as the erduite died Orshirk poped and agroed the SK. We kept Orshirk on the ramp and everyone attacked him from range. His Dot is a nasty bugger  so have ur dps move to the casters to grab heals once they get to 30% or so.<br>
<br>
 Orshirk took awhile to chop down but he died and i have my orb.<br>
<br>
<br>
  Tennir Saxx<br>
